metadata.name: Gold Bar Girl
metadata.description:
A girl in a balaclava with a gold bar in her hand.
There is undeniable confidence in her gaze.

      The golden bar fills her with hot energy.
With this powerful burst of energy the cells around her body are being renewed.

      Her consciousness changes: she is confident in wealth and looks into the distance at her new monetary goal. 

     There are no more obstacles for her to achieve this goal.

The real phys art 2538*3558
